cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CV

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with language modeling tasks such as word analogy and word similarity. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new method for training machine learning models. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with improving the performance of a popular AI model. It could also be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it evaluates the performance of the proposed model on the task of basket completion, which is a recommendation task. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the proposed model could potentially be applied to image recommendation tasks.
